---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BreadcrumbNav from '@/components/BreadcrumbNav.astro';
import CTABanner from '@/components/CTABanner.astro';
import HeroSignal from '@/components/HeroSignal.astro';
import { buildOrganizationSchema, buildPersonSchema } from '@/lib/schema';

const schemas = [buildOrganizationSchema(), buildPersonSchema()];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Agentic AI Associates — The UK's Ops-AI Specialist"
  description="Meet the team behind Agentic AI Associates. UK ops-AI consultancy for mid-market firms deploying agentic systems with measurable results. Book a free call."
  schema={schemas}
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-hero-bg)] text-[var(--color-hero-text)] section relative overflow-hidden">
    <HeroSignal variant="network" seed="about" />
    <div class="container relative">
      <BreadcrumbNav items={[{ label: 'About', href: '/about/' }]} />
      <h1 class="text-white max-w-3xl">About Us</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mt-4 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">We're AI consultants who actually build things. Not slide decks — systems.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container section-sm">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 prose">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Agentic AI Associates is a UK-based AI consultancy. We help businesses understand, adopt, and benefit from artificial intelligence. Not in five years. Now.</p>
        <p>We work with organisations of all sizes — from startups finding product-market fit to enterprises managing complex digital transformations. Our approach is practical, hands-on, and focused on outcomes.</p>

        <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
        <p><strong>We build, not just advise.</strong> Most consultancies hand you a strategy document and walk away. We stick around for implementation. We write code. We deploy systems. We measure results.</p>
        <p><strong>We speak plain English.</strong> AI is complex enough without adding consultant-speak. We explain things clearly. Short sentences. No jargon.</p>
        <p><strong>We specialise in agentic AI.</strong> The next wave of AI isn't chatbots — it's autonomous agents that handle complex workflows end to end. We're building these systems today.</p>
        <p><strong>We're UK-based.</strong> We understand UK business culture, regulations, and data protection requirements. GDPR compliance is baked into everything we do.</p>

        <h2>Our Expertise</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>AI Strategy</strong> — Roadmaps, readiness assessments, opportunity identification</li>
          <li><strong>Agentic AI</strong> — Autonomous agents, multi-step workflows, tool-use systems</li>
          <li><strong>Generative AI</strong> — LLMs, RAG architectures, prompt engineering</li>
          <li><strong>Data & AI</strong> — Pipelines, analytics, machine learning models</li>
          <li><strong>Implementation</strong> — Integration, deployment, monitoring, optimisation</li>
          <li><strong>Training</strong> — Workshops, upskilling, responsible AI adoption</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Founder</h2>
        <p><strong>Sunny Patel</strong> is the founder of Agentic AI Associates. He built this site — and it ranked on Google and generated an enterprise lead within a week of launch. That's the kind of speed and rigour he brings to client work. <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sunnypatel" rel="noopener noreferrer">Connect on LinkedIn</a>.</p>
        <p>Sunny founded Agentic AI Associates because he saw too many businesses being sold AI solutions they didn't need — or being told to wait when they should be acting. His approach is simple: understand the problem first, then apply the right technology. His track record proves it: first client (Wireless Logic, £370M PE-backed) came through inbound lead from this site within 7 days of launch. The diagnostic scoped a Quote-to-Cash automation project spanning 6 markets, 4 systems integrations, and 300+ business process steps. Board approval followed within 3 weeks.</p>

        <h3>Credentials &amp; Expertise</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Applied AI Systems:</strong> 15+ years building data pipelines, machine learning systems, and operational automation. Moved from data engineering into AI strategy and agentic systems design 2023–present.</li>
          <li><strong>Regulated Industry Depth:</strong> Extensive experience in financial services (quote-to-cash, portfolio analytics, fraud detection), manufacturing (supply chain forecasting, predictive maintenance), and insurance (claims triage, policy administration). Understands post-Brexit UK compliance landscape deeply.</li>
          <li><strong>Technical Stack:</strong> Python, LangChain, LangGraph, OpenAI, Anthropic Claude, Hugging Face, dbt, Astro, Next.js. Fluent in AWS and GCP AI services, Temporal and n8n workflow orchestration, custom agentic pipeline design.</li>
          <li><strong>Consulting Chops:</strong> Comfortable presenting to boards and C-suite, building business cases with CFO-grade ROI analysis, managing multi-team engagements, handling stakeholder risk and organisational change. Can code when necessary, but doesn't hide behind code.</li>
          <li><strong>Compliance and Trust:</strong> UK-based; fully GDPR compliant; ICO-registered data practices; PI/PL cover placed before Phase 2 engagements. Familiar with FCA requirements, NHS data governance, SRA guidance on legal AI systems, and Data Protection Act 2018.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <p><strong>Honesty first.</strong> If AI isn't right for your problem, we'll tell you. We'd rather lose a project than waste your money.</p>
        <p><strong>Ship over plan.</strong> We believe in working software over PowerPoint slides. Every engagement produces something real.</p>
        <p><strong>Measure everything.</strong> If we can't measure the impact, we haven't finished the job.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="space-y-6">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Quick Facts</h3>
          <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <div>
              <dt class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Founded</dt>
              <dd class="font-medium">2026</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Location</dt>
              <dd class="font-medium">United Kingdom</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Speciality</dt>
              <dd class="font-medium">Agentic AI & Applied AI</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Focus</dt>
              <dd class="font-medium">Mid-market UK businesses</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">See Our Results</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-5 leading-relaxed">Real outcomes from real projects — proof, not promises.</p>
          <a href="/about/results/" class="btn btn-outline text-sm w-full justify-center">View Results</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-accent)]/5 to-[var(--color-primary-light)]/5 border-[var(--color-accent)]/20">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Ready to Talk?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-5 leading-relaxed">30-minute fit call with the founder. No commitment, no jargon.</p>
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary text-sm w-full justify-center">Book a Fit Call</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABanner
    headline="Let's build something that actually works."
    text="Whether you're stepping into AI for the first time or scaling an existing programme, we'll tell you straight whether a Diagnostic is the right next move."
    buttonText="Book a Fit Call"
    buttonHref="/contact/"
  />
</BaseLayout>
